import React from 'react'; import { MDBCol, MDBContainer, MDBRow, MDBCard, MDBCardText, MDBCardBody, MDBCardImage, MDBBtn, MDBBreadcrumb, MDBBreadcrumbItem, MDBProgress, MDBProgressBar, MDBIcon, MDBListGroup, MDBListGroupItem } from 'mdb-react-ui-kit'; import { useRef } from 'react' export default function MyProfile({ user, self }) { const inputRef = useRef(null) if (!user) return null const { name, email, phone, address, birthday } = user let avatar = 'https://mdbcdn.b-cdn.net/img/Photos/new-templates/bootstrap-chat/ava3.webp'; const date = new Date(birthday).toLocaleDateString() const handleUpload = () => { inputRef.current.click(); } const handleFileChange = async event => { const fileObj = event.target.files && event.target.files[0]; if (!fileObj) { return; } event.target.value = null; const base64 = await convertToBase64(fileObj) console.log(base64) } const convertToBase64 = (file) => { return new Promise((resolve, reject) => { const fileReader = new FileReader(); fileReader.readAsDataURL(file); fileReader.onload = () => { resolve(avatar); }; fileReader.onerror = (error) => { console.log("here") reject(error); }; }) } return (
User Profile

Full Stack Developer

Bay Area, San Francisco, CA

{!self ? ( <> Add Friend Message ) : ( <> { handleUpload() }}>Upload Avatar )}
https://mdbootstrap.com mdbootstrap @mdbootstrap mdbootstrap mdbootstrap Full Name {name}
Email {email}
Phone {phone}
Birthday {date}
Address {address}
); }
